{"tid":442631,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港之光】而家直播緊香港Rainbow Six隊出戰悉尼","createTime":"2017-10-20T22:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T09:58:21.000Z","uid":35990,"like":65,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4f91c0238e2649e6bef56d30654555a9806c53a6","tid":442631,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T22:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/063439_9b35acd0fb39b595056b5f31478dcb85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F063439_9b35acd0fb39b595056b5f31478dcb85.jpg&h=167cf696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真．香港隊 Unique Monster 早已打入Rainbow Six職業聯賽<br />\n之前一直喺東南亞區作賽，不過今日就係喺悉尼同成個亞太區打！<br />\n佢地冇人識，冇媒體宣傳，冇贊助商支持<br />\n但係佢地都行到呢步，唔支持下點得？<br />\n<br />\n而呢個APAC Finals嚟講<br />\n最終獲勝嘅兩支隊伍下月將前往巴西參加全球總冠軍賽<br />\n<br />\nUbisoft 官方廣東話評述：<br />\nYouTube &gt;&gt; <a href=\"http://youtube.com/UbisoftSEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FUbisoftSEA&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=836d59a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/UbisoftSEA</a><br />\nTwtich &gt;&gt; <a href=\"http://twitch.tv/UbisoftSEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitch.tv%2FUbisoftSEA&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=dfc18b8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitch.tv/UbisoftSEA</a><br />\nFacebook &gt;&gt; <a href=\"http://facebook.com/Ubisoft.HKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FUbisoft.HKG&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1c6831a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/Ubisoft.HKG</a>"},{"pid":"32f25627fa1bf75b4d741eec309a06caf25aa18d","tid":442631,"uid":35990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T22:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/064051_8ddf69a289b6d2818c0f99f10f407129.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb